These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, pear
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | mirinda |
| Food       | cucumber | pear |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola | coffee |
| Sport      | climbing     | weightlifting  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, satire
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, argentine
1. the russian is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | satire  |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
