There 2 different types of food: zucchini, watermelon
1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Food       | watermelon | zucchini |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
