There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, russian
1. the russian is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | country    |
| Nationality   | colombian | russian |

