.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican
2 different pets are kept: frog, horse
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | mexican |
| Pet           | horse     | frog  |

