.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, video-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, entrepreneur
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | video-games | card-games |
| Job     | lawyer        | entrepreneur |

