.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, car
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |
| Sport       | golf  | basketball |
| Transport   | quad-bike | car |

