1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing   | filmmaking |
| Sport   | tennis | biathlon   |

 